        {
            "title": "觀塘停車場貨車遇竊 失200萬元電子鎖零件 天眼建功兩男賊落網",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"觀塘停車場貨車遇竊 失200萬元電子鎖零件 天眼建功兩男賊落網\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3fe803697581bb78e4f88323d57f4226/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022018181558291.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">觀塘停車場貨車遇竊 失200萬元電子鎖零件 天眼建功兩男賊落網</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>觀塘海濱道停車場內一部貨車2月10日遇竊，賊人從沒鎖好的車尾廂內，偷走5箱約值200萬元的電子鎖零件。經過深入調查及翻查大量閉路電視後，警方成功鎖定3名疑犯，於2月18至19日分別在羅湖及沙田，拘捕其中兩名本地男子，並起回部份約70萬元失物。\n\n</p>\n<p>觀塘警區重案組第一隊偵緝督察梁曼宜提到，被捕兩男分別39歲報稱任職司機，及30歲報稱無業。他們正被扣查，稍後警方將落案起訴相關罪名，案件明日（2月21日）在觀塘法院提堂。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4093397/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方展示所得證物。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0c0415401a4f426718b0305c4e536e30/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250220_180014546_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方展示所得證物。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4093383/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/224a1adfee2cae1a7862bd982cba1933/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250220_180014546_11.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4093384/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"被盜的電子鎖零件約值200萬元。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c2b1475dcb8a9fd597febe99c77ab75c/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250220_180014546_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        被盜的電子鎖零件約值200萬元。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4093385/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/35305be37b9669e873bcb63f7efcc84c/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250220_180014546_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4093386/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05f5fffb66af1a362a7f542c67ffc118/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250220_180014546_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4093381/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"觀塘警區重案組第一隊偵緝督察梁曼宜。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/45973f395db4c298898c35aa737eade1/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250220_175556189_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        觀塘警區重案組第一隊偵緝督察梁曼宜。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4093382/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c7a3379376a2ab0da4ed16120a2a4e4c/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250220_175556189_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>警方呼籲，駕駛者停泊時要鎖好門窗，避免將貴重財物留在車內，亦可加裝車內攝錄器；如有需要，送貨公司亦應派人看守財物，以免被不法之徒有機可乘。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方亦補充，除現場搜證外，涉案車輛附近行車紀錄儀，以及警方於罪案黑點安裝的防罪閉路電視系統，亦成功協助警方調查。截至2024年底，天眼系統已協助警方偵破122宗案件，例如兇殺、行劫、爆竊等。此外警方分析顯示，天眼系統安裝後，街道犯罪活動有所下跌，證明系統對防罪滅罪有正面作用。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
